---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
import en from '../../i18n/en.json'
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About us — Flexen"
  description="The story behind Flexen: Why we're building an AI-powered health app that combines fitness, nutrition, sleep and mental health in one place."
  locale="en"
  canonicalPath="/en/about"
>

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="section gradient-hero min-h-[70vh] flex items-center pt-32">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <span class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium gradient-accent text-white mb-6 reveal">Our story</span>
        <h1 class="text-[length:var(--text-hero)] font-bold mb-6 reveal">
          The story behind Flexen
        </h1>
        <p class="text-secondary text-[length:var(--text-body)] mx-auto mb-8 reveal">
          Flexen was born from a simple frustration: Why do you need 5 apps when one can do it all? Calorie counter here, workout planner there, sleep tracker over there — and none of them talk to each other. We wanted to change that.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mission Section -->
  <section class="section" id="mission">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-[length:var(--text-h2)] font-bold mb-6 reveal">
              Holistic health, accessible to everyone
            </h2>
            <p class="text-secondary text-[length:var(--text-body)] mb-4 reveal">
              Our vision: combine AI with health data so that everyone has access to a personal coach — not just those who can afford a trainer.
            </p>
            <p class="text-secondary text-[length:var(--text-body)] reveal">
              Living a holistically healthy life shouldn't require five different subscriptions. Flexen brings together nutrition, training, sleep, mental health and AI coaching in a single app. Personal. Intelligent. Affordable.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl gradient-card border border-white/5 reveal">
            <blockquote class="text-[length:var(--text-body)] italic text-secondary">
              &ldquo;Health is not a luxury. Everyone deserves a coach who knows their data, understands their goals, and is available around the clock.&rdquo;
            </blockquote>
            <p class="mt-4 text-flexen-accent font-semibold text-[length:var(--text-small)]">— The Flexen Team</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What makes Flexen different -->
  <section class="section" id="difference">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content">
        <h2 class="text-[length:var(--text-h2)] font-bold text-center mb-4 reveal">
          What makes Flexen different
        </h2>
        <p class="text-secondary text-[length:var(--text-body)] text-center mb-16 max-w-2xl mx-auto reveal">
          Three principles that guide everything we build.
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 stagger-children">
          <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl gradient-card border border-white/5 card-hover gradient-border">
            <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium gradient-accent text-white mb-4">AI-Powered</span>
            <h3 class="text-[length:var(--text-h3)] font-bold mb-3">AI as a coach, not a gimmick</h3>
            <p class="text-secondary text-[length:var(--text-body)]">
              Julio isn't a marketing feature. He has access to your data and can take real action: create plans, analyze progress, make recommendations. A real coach that keeps learning.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl gradient-card border border-white/5 card-hover gradient-border">
            <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-success/20 text-success mb-4">Holistic</span>
            <h3 class="text-[length:var(--text-h3)] font-bold mb-3">Holistic, not fragmented</h3>
            <p class="text-secondary text-[length:var(--text-body)]">
              Nutrition affects sleep. Sleep affects training. Training affects mood. Flexen understands these connections — because all your data lives in one place.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl gradient-card border border-white/5 card-hover gradient-border">
            <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-flexen-accent/20 text-flexen-accent mb-4">Privacy</span>
            <h3 class="text-[length:var(--text-h3)] font-bold mb-3">Your data belongs to you</h3>
            <p class="text-secondary text-[length:var(--text-body)]">
              Health data is the most personal data there is. We don't sell it, we don't share it, and we never will. Your data stays your data. Period.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Tech/AI Section -->
  <section class="section" id="technology">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-[length:var(--text-h2)] font-bold text-center mb-4 reveal">
          The technology behind Flexen
        </h2>
        <p class="text-secondary text-[length:var(--text-body)] text-center mb-16 max-w-2xl mx-auto reveal">
          Cutting-edge AI, seamlessly integrated into your daily life.
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-6 stagger-children">
          <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl gradient-card border border-white/5 card-hover flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 items-start">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl gradient-accent flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 9a2 2 0 012-2h.93a2 2 0 001.664-.89l.812-1.22A2 2 0 0110.07 4h3.86a2 2 0 011.664.89l.812 1.22A2 2 0 0018.07 7H19a2 2 0 012 2v9a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V9z" />
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 13a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-[length:var(--text-h3)] font-bold mb-2">Computer vision for food recognition</h3>
              <p class="text-secondary text-[length:var(--text-body)]">
                Flexen's AI analyzes photos of your meals in real time. Over 10,000 foods are recognized — with calories, macros and portion sizes. No manual entry, no guessing.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl gradient-card border border-white/5 card-hover flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 items-start">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl gradient-accent flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8 10h.01M12 10h.01M16 10h.01M9 16H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v8a2 2 0 01-2 2h-5l-5 5v-5z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-[length:var(--text-h3)] font-bold mb-2">LLM with function calling for Julio</h3>
              <p class="text-secondary text-[length:var(--text-body)]">
                Julio is more than a chatbot. Through function calling, he can actively access your data and take action: create workout plans, analyze meals, detect sleep patterns — all through natural language.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl gradient-card border border-white/5 card-hover flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 items-start">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl gradient-accent flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-[length:var(--text-h3)] font-bold mb-2">Health Connect & HealthKit integration</h3>
              <p class="text-secondary text-[length:var(--text-body)]">
                Flexen connects seamlessly with your smartphone's health ecosystem. Sleep, steps, heart rate — everything flows together automatically. No additional wearable needed.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Final CTA -->
  <section class="section gradient-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content text-center">
        <h2 class="text-[length:var(--text-h1)] font-bold mb-6 reveal">{en.finalCta.headline}</h2>
        <p class="text-secondary text-[length:var(--text-body)] mx-auto mb-8 reveal">{en.finalCta.subline}</p>
        <a href="#" class="btn-glow inline-flex items-center justify-center px-10 py-4 rounded-xl gradient-accent text-white font-semibold text-lg transition-transform hover:scale-[1.02] active:scale-[0.97] reveal">{en.finalCta.cta}</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
